OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather cloudy start but sunny
OL,6,Fspells developing through the morning.
OL,7,FStaying dry in the afternoon with some
OL,8,Fsunshine and light winds. Cloud
OL,9,Fbuilding later in the day for Orkney.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDespite a sunny evening for
OL,12,FShetland cloud will build with some
OL,13,Frain spreading north from, chance of
OL,14,Fthunder for Orkney. Some brighter
OL,15,Fspells for Orkney by morning.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FA cloudy start to the
OL,18,Fweekend but chance of some bright or
OL,19,Fsunny spells, a warm day, perhaps some
OL,20,Fshowers for Orkney later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
