OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FEarly
OL,6,Frain on Sunday clearing east, brighter
OL,7,Fspells in the afternoon. Becoming
OL,8,Fwindy on Monday with a few light
OL,9,Fshowers, less windy on Tuesday with
OL,10,Fmainly dry weather.
